            "root_cause_hypothesis": "The QueryProfiler class is not thread-safe, leading to potential data races and inconsistent profiling results when accessed concurrently.",
            "fix_logic": "Synchronize key public methods (getProfileBreakdown and getTree) to ensure thread-safe access to shared mutable state, and reduce visibility of helper methods to private to limit external access and potential misuse.",
